#: ../content/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"This package introduces a feature in which ConfigItems and their "
"interconnections, as well as their related tickets, can be geographically "
"represented on a map through the `OpenStreetMap <https://https://"
"www.openstreetmap.org/>`_ platform."
msgstr ""

